%h1 Quick Reference

- pages_for_quick_ref.each do |category, pages|

  %h2
    = link_to category.titlecase, "##{category}"

  %table.quickref
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Usage
        %th Supported Methods
        %th URL

    %tbody
      - pages.each do |page|
        %tr
          %td.usage
            = link_to page.title, "##{page.anchor}"
          %td.method
            = page.methods.map{|m| m.to_s.upcase}.join(', ')
          %td.url
            = page.endpoint


